{"type":"article","id":14410,"title":"2020.02.13 00:00，悼念李文亮，全民换头像。","uid":5339,"topics":[6271,6495],"contents":"李文亮在網上披露武漢醫院有多名肺炎病患，是披露疫情的「吹哨者」，但及後被武漢當局指他造謠，早前感染新型肺炎死亡。<br>\n中國政府的昏庸、專制及封建壓制了公布疫情風險，違反人權及言論自由，導致人民需要付上生命代價，亦引致全民恐慌。政府应立即歸還人民言論自由、追究失職官員，並撤回對李醫生的指控。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/w2voQQI.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/w2voQQI.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/w2voQQI.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/dUs2HoH.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dUs2HoH.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/dUs2HoH.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/0QBiqtA.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0QBiqtA.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/0QBiqtA.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-02-12","agreeCount":14,"discussionCount":0}